Hello everyone,
Well I post this because since July 1st I did a lsd bad trip,
I want to say that before this bad trip I used to hit 20 bowls a day and one w.k every two months with hardcore stuff(E,coke,lsd, and everything else)...For 3 years,
now I'll tell you how it went.
a Great w.k was ahead
on friday night everything was alright
we took 5gr of speed and all the md,
saturday morning after an all nighter I go to work only in the morning from 9 to 12 in the afternoon ,
we went on,
As for me I carried on hitting bowls and hitting speed,
a coworker hands me the drink with a drop from the lsd vial
first I hesitated but then I thought come on take it(which I shouldn't have) .
the night goes on normally and the other so called coworkers had decided to make us spin out great coworkers.....
this much vaunted beach was crowded and one of the two coworkers tells us some people are looking for trouble and we're gonna fight ....
I tell myself the product has to come down bc I won't be able to fight as is
so that means I forced myself to resist the product,
there, the paranoia began to overwhelm me while directing a stageplay
the other two coworkers who hadn't take anything , start provoking the guys that are mad at us
me while totally spaced out I tell myself it will spin out of control any time now,
time goes by nothing happens.
anyway we leave the beach and we go to my place,
I ask them whether the guys are following us,
they don't answer,
we get at my place and there they all leave me alone at home with my girlfriend sleeping...,
my bad goes on all night
no way to sleep,I'm overthinking and I'm out with a bat at the faintest noise...
the sun is rising and I begin to sleep because I had just realized there was nothing,
the night goes normally ,
I get up and I'm still having the effect of LSD and everything
I'm thinking it's normal
so it was Sunday and I had to work the next day.
the day goes normally
I hit a few bowls then I crash out ,
Sunday passes and Monday comes
I still feel queasy ,
I still tell myself it's normal considering I fell flat on the face....
so at 2 pm I was supposed to start working
there I eat a bit and I hit a big line of speed to feel great at work...
so I take the car and then I go to work
once at work , as soon as I open the store I'm starting to feel dizzy my heart starts racing at 200 and I feel I'm gonna faint ,
reassuring myself I go buying snikers bars and something to drink,
then I go back to work and another crisis...
freaked out I call my mum.. because the coworkers weren't there ....
then my mum takes me to the doctor
he asks me what I've done and I spill everything
and my mum took it pretty good well she knew I was shady..
The Doctor tells me to wait for the product to come down it will take a few months and that's all,
I told him I had vision trouble
I told him I had vision trouble
he said it was normal too and that it would come down,
for my anxiety attack he ordered lizanxia an anti axiolitit well for anxiety ,
I take 1 morning 1 the evening,
it soothes me but the voices in my head don't stop,
